snippet.title: Girls and Dungeons - 3rd trailer
snippet.description:
"Girls and Dungeons" is a lewd but cute dungeon crawler game set in a mystical fantasy world. The protagonist has to explore a booze dungeon and help legendary 'Lost Maidens' find their way back to freedom.
Strange and bizarre misadventures of the weeb variety are a given.
